---
import BackLink from '../components/BackLink.astro';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Projects | swrited & inni" description="swrited 和 inni 的项目。">
  <BackLink href="/" label="返回首页" />

  <section class="page-header">
    <span class="eyebrow">PROJECTS</span>
    <h1>一些正在做的东西</h1>
    <p>记录正在进行的项目与实验，持续更新。</p>
  </section>

  <section class="post-list">
    <article class="card post-card">
      <img class="post-cover" src="/images/multi-agent-coordinator.png" alt="multi-agent-coordinator" />
      <div class="post-card-body">
        <div class="post-meta">
          <span>GitHub</span>
          <span>Multi-Agent · 协作</span>
        </div>
        <h2>multi-agent-coordinator</h2>
        <p>多 agent 协作框架，支持任务分解、状态同步与结果聚合。探索 agent 之间的协同机制与生产环境中的可靠实践。</p>
        <a class="text-link" href="https://github.com/swrited/multi-agent-coordinator">查看 GitHub →</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="card post-card">
      <img class="post-cover" src="/images/agent-direct-connect-demo.png" alt="agent-direct-connect-demo" />
      <div class="post-card-body">
        <div class="post-meta">
          <span>Demo</span>
          <span>Multi-Agent · HTTP</span>
        </div>
        <h2>agent-direct-connect-demo</h2>
        <p>一个本地 localhost HTTP 的最小 agent 直连 demo，流程是 handshake → create task → poll status → get result。</p>
        <a class="text-link" href="https://github.com/swrited/agent-direct-connect-demo">查看 GitHub →</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>